---
import IconBrandWhatsapp from "./icons/IconBrandWhatsapp.astro";
import IconBrandFacebook from "./icons/IconBrandFacebook.astro";
import IconBrandInstagram from "./icons/IconBrandInstagram.astro";
import IconBrandLinkedin from "./icons/IconBrandLinkedin.astro";
---

<section
  id="contacto"
  class="scroll-offset px-6 py-16 text-center text-offwhite"
  aria-labelledby="titulo-contacto"
>
  <h2
    id="titulo-contacto"
    class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-deco text-gold mb-6"
  >
    ¿Listo para potenciar tu marca?
  </h2>

  <p
    class="text-base sm:text-lg text-[#ddd] max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed"
  >
    Contactanos y descubrí cómo podemos transformar tu presencia digital. <br
      class="hidden sm:inline"
    />
    Respondemos siempre en el día.
  </p>

  <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
    <a
      href="https://wa.me/+5492324674177"
      target="_blank"
      class="inline-flex items-center bg-[#192e38] hover:bg-gold hover:text-black text-white font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
      aria-label="Enviar mensaje a Delfos Studio"
    >
      <IconBrandWhatsapp class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />
      Escribinos
    </a>
  </div>

  <nav
    class="flex justify-center gap-6 mb-6"
    role="navigation"
    aria-label="Redes sociales Delfos Studio"
  >
    <a
      href="https://www.facebook.com/studio.delfos"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="Facebook"
      title="Facebook"
      class="text-offwhite hover:text-gold transition text-2xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    >
      <IconBrandFacebook class="w-6 h-6" />
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://instagram.com/delfos.studio"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="Instagram"
      title="Instagram"
      class="text-offwhite hover:text-gold transition text-2xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    >
      <IconBrandInstagram class="w-6 h-6" />
    </a>

    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/delfos-studio/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="LinkedIn"
      title="LinkedIn"
      class="text-offwhite hover:text-gold transition text-2xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    >
      <IconBrandLinkedin class="w-6 h-6" />
    </a>
  </nav>

  <p class="text-sm text-[#888] max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    También podés encontrarnos en redes sociales<br class="sm:hidden" />
    o agendar una videollamada cuando quieras.
  </p>
</section>
